<h2>Appearance</h2>
<p>Modify theme and display settings</p>
<hr />
<div class="card-div setting-bg border-radius-5">
    <h3>Theme Manager</h3>
    <div class="theme-toggle-container">
        <p>Enable dark theme: <i class='bx bx-help-circle' 
            title="Switch between light and dark mode to match your preference or improve visibility."></i></p>

        <label class="theme-switch">
